reviewText: I first saw Rhapsody on BET and back then I was using VHS so I recorded it, then my VCR broke and DVD became the "it thing" so I decided to purchase Rhapsody on DVD.  The DVD plays wonderfully, no scratches or skips in the movie.  I have recommended Amazon.com to several people to buy movies.  I love it.  For some reason I cant click the rating button, but I give this 5 stars.

reviewText: Record producer Dollar Bill and his girlfriend Lenore are completely in love. They live the good life, despite the mounting pressures on Bill to stay true to music as an art form. But as the pressures mount, Bill's sexy ex shows up. A successful singer, she poses a real threat to his life with Lenore. I enjoyed the movie tremendously especially the music in the movie. A good variety of actors/actresses in the movie. Lisa Raye is a good actress.
